PrecisAmendments (SCHEDULE No. 262) to the MOTOR VEHICLE SAFETY REGULATIONS which will require that a head restraint be provided at each front outboard seating position in trucks, multi-purpose passenger vehicles (vans) and buses having a gross vehicle weight rating of less than 4,536 kilograms.

precis:
Amendments (SCHEDULE No. 262) to the MOTOR VEHICLE SAFETY REGULATIONS which
will require that a head restraint be provided at each front outboard
seating position in trucks, multi-purpose passenger vehicles (vans) and
buses having a gross vehicle weight rating of less than 4,536 kilograms.
